<div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-4 py-8">
  <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow p-6">
    <div class="mb-6">
      <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 flex items-center gap-2">
        <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-red-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 9v2m0 4h.01m-6.938 4h13.856c1.54 0 2.502-1.667 1.732-3L13.732 4c-.77-1.333-2.694-1.333-3.464 0L3.34 16c-.77 1.333.192 3 1.732 3z"></path>
        </svg>
        通報する
      </h1>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-2">
        不適切なコンテンツやユーザーを見つけた場合は、以下のフォームからご報告ください。
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- 通報対象 -->
    <div class="mb-6 p-4 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg">
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-1">通報対象</p>
      <p class="font-medium text-gray-800">
        <% case @target %>
        <% when Job %>
          <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-green-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 13.255A23.931 23.931 0 0112 15c-3.183 0-6.22-.62-9-1.745M16 6V4a2 2 0 00-2-2h-4a2 2 0 00-2 2v2m4 6h.01M5 20h14a2 2 0 002-2V8a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z"></path>
            </svg>
            求人: <%= @target.title %>
          </span>
        <% when User %>
          <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M16 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0zM12 14a7 7 0 00-7 7h14a7 7 0 00-7-7z"></path>
            </svg>
            ユーザー: <%= @target.name %>
          </span>
        <% end %>
      </p>
    </div>

    <%= form_with model: @report, url: reports_path(target_type: @target_type, target_id: @target_id), local: true, class: "space-y-6" do |f| %>
      <% if @report.errors.any? %>
        <div class="bg-red-100 border border-red-400 text-red-700 px-4 py-3 rounded">
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside">
            <% @report.errors.full_messages.each do |message| %>
              <li><%= message %></li>
            <% end %>
          </ul>
        </div>
      <% end %>

      <div>
        <%= f.label :reason, "通報理由", class: "block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-2" %>
        <div class="space-y-2">
          <% Report::REASON_LABELS.each do |key, label| %>
            <label class="flex items-center p-3 border rounded-lg cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 transition">
              <%= f.radio_button :reason, key, class: "h-4 w-4 text-red-600 focus:ring-red-500 border-gray-300" %>
              <span class="ml-3 text-gray-700"><%= label %></span>
            </label>
          <% end %>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div>
        <%= f.label :description, "詳細（任意）", class: "block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1" %>
        <%= f.text_area :description, rows: 4,
            class: "w-full px-4 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg focus:ring-red-500 focus:border-red-500",
            placeholder: "具体的な状況や問題点があれば記入してください" %>
      </div>

      <div class="flex gap-4">
        <%= f.submit "通報する", class: "flex-1 py-3 px-4 border border-transparent rounded-lg shadow-sm text-sm font-medium text-white bg-red-600 hover:bg-red-700 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-red-500 cursor-pointer" %>
        <%= link_to "キャンセル", :back, class: "flex-1 py-3 px-4 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg shadow-sm text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 bg-white hover:bg-gray-50 text-center" %>
      </div>
    <% end %>

    <p class="mt-6 text-xs text-gray-500">
      ※ 通報内容は管理者が確認し、適切に対応いたします。虚偽の通報を繰り返した場合、アカウント停止の対象となる場合があります。
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
